==English==

===Pronunciation===
* /ˈheɪˌsid/  (GenAm)

===Etymology===
From '''[[hay]]''' + '''[[seed]]'''.

===Noun===
'''hayseed''' ''(uncountable or countable; plural:'' [[hayseeds]])

# [[seed|Seed]]s from grass that has become hay.
# [[cruft|Cruft]] from bits of hay that sticks to clothing, etc.
# ''(only countable)'' A [[rustic]] person; a [[yokel]] or [[bumpkin]].  [Also used attributively: e.g. a ''hayseed'' name.]